Blocks.Text: For value received, SRP 2013-7, LLC, whose address is 601 BRICKELL KEY DR., SUITE 700, MIAMI, FL, 33131
(herein "Assignor") does hereby grant, sell, assign, transfer and convey, unto ATC2021 TRUST, whose address is
C/O RICHLAND & FALKOWSKI, PLLC, 5 FAIRLAWN DRIVE, STE 204, WASHINGTONVILLE, NY, 10992 (herein
"Assignee") all interest under that certain Mortgage Dated: 6/17/1999, in the amount of $42,400.00, executed by
JOHN WESLEY SEE AND JACQUELINE IDA SEE HUSBAND AND WIFE to CONTIMORTGAGE CORPORATION
and Recorded: 9/13/1999, Book: 127, Page: 147 in LAWRENCE County, State of Kentucky.
TO HAVE AND TO HOLD, the same unto Assignee, its successors and assigns, forever, subject only to the terms
and conditions of the above-described Mortgage.
On January 28, 2022, before me, Jessica Brown, a Notary Public in and for STONE in the State of MISSOURI,
personally appeared KALEENA OGO, ASSISTANT VICE PRESIDENT, SRP 2013-7, LLC, personally known to me
(or proved to me on the basis of satisfactory evidence) to be the person(s) whose name(s) is/are subscribed to the
within instrument and acknowledged to me by means of X physical presence or online notarization, that
he/she/they executed the same in his/her/their authorized capacity, and that by his/her/their signature on the
instrument the person, or the entity upon behalf of which the person acted, executed the instrument.
KY/LAWRENCE Jessica Brown Richmond Monroe Group Inc. P.O Boy 458,Kindoeding it, MOLISINE
